1
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:13,680
What's going on?

2
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:15,440
Didn't you ask me to check Ye Zhiqiu's

3
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:16,760
flight itinerary at the airline?

4
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:18,920
He didn't leave.

5
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:21,000
He did book a ticket to go abroad,

6
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:22,760
but I found out that

7
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:24,640
someone else was on the same flight.

8
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:26,520
Zhang Xiaoshao.

9
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:30,880
You think Ye Zhiqiu and Zhang Xiaoshao

10
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:31,880
are in this together?

11
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:33,320
I called him right away,

12
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,040
but he didn't answer.

13
00:00:34,680 --> 00:00:36,360
So I went to check the paintings.

14
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:37,960
They were all gone.

15
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,200
If that's the case,

16
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:42,360
he must have taken the paintings.

17
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:43,200
I suspected

18
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,440
his motives from the beginning.

19
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:46,040
Why would he spend money

20
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:47,160
to help you seek revenge

21
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:48,200
against someone

22
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,480
as dangerous as Zhen Shida?

23
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,600
I don't believe he's that kind of person.

24
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:56,000
I'll go get him now.

25
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,000
and ask him yourself.

26
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,680
Wait.

27
00:00:58,880 --> 00:00:59,920
I know where he is.

28
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,400
I'll go find him.

29
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,200
Give me a cup.

30
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,200
If you had been five minutes later,

31
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,360
I would have left.

32
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,960
You wouldn't.

33
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,840
Since you could wait for me

34
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,720
in a place I could guess,

35
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,560
it proves I was right about you.

36
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,200
Jia Yu must think

37
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,200
I've run away with those paintings,

38
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,080
right?

39
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,600
If he sees you now,

40
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,680
you won't be able to leave.

41
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,600
Those paintings

42
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,360
are stored

43
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,400
with a reliable friend.

44
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,160
When we find a buyer,

45
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,720
the money will be deposited

46
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,800
in the account of the Memory Tree Project

47
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,320
and the Victims Alliance.

48
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,120
Why are you leaving?

49
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,080
Don't forget,

50
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,920
we have a contract.

51
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,680
You broke it first.

52
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,040
I didn't.

53
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,720
You didn't?

54
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,920
I still don't know who you are.

55
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,240
Isn't that breaking the contract?

56
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,280
Do you know what this is?

57
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,640
This is a card my idol wrote for me

58
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,880
on my birthday two years ago.

59
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,280
I've never met him,

60
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,160
but I've played games with him for years.

61
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:57,760
I know

62
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,680
this is his favorite

63
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,360
Mangyin Future.

64
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,560
And you?

65
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,480
You don't even know who they are.

66
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,000
There must be his DNA

67
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,040
on this card.

68
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,280
Do you dare to take one of your hairs

69
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,040
and go with me to verify it now?

70
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:15,640
Do you dare?

71
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,960
That's right.

72
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,560
I'm not Hao Qing.

73
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,840
Then who are you?

74
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,960
I'm Hao Feng,

75
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,600
Hao Qing's twin brother.

76
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,480
Twins?

77
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,280
Brother,

78
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,680
the receptionist mistook me for you,

79
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,560
so I used your keycard to enter your room.

80
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,560
Come back quickly.

81
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,360
I'll wait for you.

82
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,520
Impossible.

83
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,560
Absolutely impossible.

84
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,200
This person in the video

85
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,960
doesn't look like you at all.

86
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,080
You're not twins at all.

87
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,640
We used to look exactly the same.

88
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,399
That's why he became my scapegoat.

89
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,920
Bro, you're back.

90
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,160
Give me back the key card.

91
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,360
Don't impersonate me again.

92
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,680
The receptionist made a mistake.

93
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:26,640
Bro.

94
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,960
How's your research on Memory Tree

95
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:28,480
going?

96
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,920
It's going well.

97
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,040
That's good.

98
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,200
I'm going out for a while.

99
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,320
Wait for me in the room.

100
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,400
Yes, sir.

101
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,240
Investor Zhen Shida

102
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,080
made a statement on the Memory Tree Fund

103
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,080
explosion incident.

104
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,720
I did notice Hao Feng

105
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,720
had recently developed a gambling habit,

106
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,760
which led to the Memory Tree project

107
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,040
being stuck.

108
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,840
Of course, I have also tried to dissuade him.

109
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,520
Meanwhile,

110
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,920
I'm using legal means

111
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,200
to withdraw the investment.

112
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,960
But I still failed to

113
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,400
recover losses in time.

114
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,280
I deeply apologize.

115
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,160
Meanwhile,

116
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,760
I'll continue to cooperate with the police

117
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,800
until the whole thing is clear.

118
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,480
The huge amount of money

119
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,320
is unknown with Hao Feng's

120
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,560
suicide.

121
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,000
This involves an underground casino

122
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,600
and cross-border transfer.

123
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,560
According to legal experts,

124
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,520
it's difficult to retrieve the funds.

125
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,600
The evidence chain is currently missing.

126
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,480
Zhen Shida wanted to kill me,

127
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,920
but my twin brother died instead.

128
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,920
Hao Qing.

129
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:09,480
This is the only thing

130
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,760
Hao Qing left me.

131
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,560
But I let him lose his life because of me.

132
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,160
So,

133
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,440
actually, I never

134
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:25,640
met my idol, right?

135
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,360
I did lie to you.

136
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,000
But I need financial support

137
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,160
to complete my revenge plan.

138
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,760
I saw your brother's game ID.

139
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,560
I saw your message.

140
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,160
I investigated your identity.

141
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,920
The Zhang Group's useless heir.

142
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,640
A person who has nothing but money.

143
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,440
After everything is over,

144
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,160
the money we took from Zhen Shida,

145
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,560
to compensate the victims,

146
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,920
I'll give you back

147
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,680
what you've paid according to the contract.

148
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,920
Of course,

149
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,720
you can also choose to quit now.

150
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:11,320
Do you think I care about money?

151
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,960
Now that I know the truth,

152
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,160
you can't kick me out.

153
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,360
I don't care if you're Hao Qing or Hao Feng.

154
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,960
We've been working together for so long.

155
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,880
I've already treated you as my best brother.

156
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,520
And this time, it's not just revenge.

157
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,920
We also want to

158
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,560
seek justice for those who were hurt

159
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,920
for no reason.

160
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,559
Trust me.

161
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,440
This time,

162
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,919
let's do something for him together.

163
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,880
I know it's very dangerous.

164
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,600
But I never intended

165
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,880
to sacrifice you in my plan.

166
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:41,840
Please believe me on this.

167
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:47,360
Do you really think I'm afraid of Zhen Shida?

168
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,720
I'm Zhang Xiaoshao.

169
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,040
One more thing.

170
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,320
My real identity.

171
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,960
You're the only one who knows it.

172
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,400
Please keep it a secret.

173
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:09,000
Okay?

174
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,720
Why didn't you tell Jia Yu?

175
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,720
Aren't you best friends?

176
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,440
It's too complicated.

177
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,560
He also lost his memory in the accident.

178
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,440
I don't want to make things worse.

179
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,760
I just let him believe

180
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,400
that Hao Feng is dead.
